  "instructions": [
    "Heat a pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the pork burger patties and cook for 3-4 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "While the burgers are cooking, toast the burger buns in the pan.",
    "Wok-fry the onions by heating a small amount of oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onions to the pan and cook until softened, stirring frequently.",
